{"tid":1463757,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不要只是叫口號，嘗試先幫助旅客","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:03.000Z","uid":58117,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"747578264cdd575fbfec44c2cb98c3bcae046d20","tid":1463757,"uid":58117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"係fb見到薯伯伯分享機場所見嘅事，有啲睇法（少開post，大家屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，大家一齊討論下：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 旅客一出離境大堂見到咁多人，難免會驚。各位可以嘗試用自己識嘅語言<span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫助佢地</span>，教佢地點出市區或者介紹唱錢、買電話卡、住宿地方等，俾佢地感覺<span style=\"font-size: large;\">友善同helpful<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>，人地都係想輕鬆去下旅行。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 要其他國家旅客係短短離開機場嘅路程知道香港政治事件好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可以嘗試<span style=\"font-size: large;\">講出重點</span>：警察濫捕、政府莫視民意等。再送上有qr code嘅單張，可以俾佢地係車程度睇。<br />\n<br />\n3/ 嘗試用劉德華嘅最佳服務態度講：唔好意思阻住你，但都祝你有個開心嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上想溝佢咁嘅笑容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">溫柔係最大嘅武力</span><br />\n<br />\n文章傳送門（申：有啲長）👉🏼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2007814566118012/posts/2589299104636219?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2007814566118012%2Fposts%2F2589299104636219%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BlScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=a0ecad17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2007814566118012/posts/2589299104636219?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8e062a7694b076d6720193d119b53fafafb36fb9","tid":1463757,"uid":58117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5e0156f1b5b1757fd88f9e9d88e37872dea161","tid":1463757,"uid":58117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset